OL,3,CCare worker, 23, jailed for rioting in
OL,4,Cuniform in post-Southport disorder
OL,6,FA care worker has been jailed after
OL,7,Fbeing caught making racist comments on
OL,8,Fa TikTok livestream during the summer
OL,9,Friots in Tamworth.
OL,11,FCameron Bell, who's 23-years-old, was
OL,12,Fcaught on CCTV wearing her work
OL,13,Funiform with around 20 people, making
OL,14,Ftheir way through Tamworth town centre
OL,15,Farmed with planks of wood and metal on
OL,16,Fthe night of August 4.
OL,18,FStafford Crown Court heard how Bell,
OL,19,Fof Worthing Grove, Tamworth, was heard
OL,20,Fswearing while referring to asylum
OL,21,Fseekers as ''tramps''.
