OL,6,FBell admitted to violent disorder in
OL,7,FSeptember and has been in custody ever
OL,8,Fsince. Her lawyer, Stephen Rudge told
OL,9,Fthe court she was ''on the periphery''
OL,10,Fof a non-confrontational group.
OL,12,F'You have lost your job as a carer'
OL,14,FPassing Sentence, Judge John Edwards
OL,15,Frejected a community order and told
OL,16,FBell that members of the group, which
OL,17,Fwas caught on CCTV near to a statue of
OL,18,FSir Robert Peel, were armed and
OL,19,Fplainly intent on further violence.
