OL,3,CCare worker, 23, jailed for rioting in
OL,4,Cuniform in post-Southport disorder
OL,6,FThe judge said: "In early August a
OL,7,Fseries of disturbances erupted across
OL,8,Fthis country following a tragic
OL,9,Fincident in late July when three young
OL,10,Fgirls were fatally stabbed at a dance
OL,11,Fclass in Southport."
OL,13,FHe adds: "The violence was fuelled by
OL,14,Fmisinformation and misplaced far-right
OL,15,Fsentiment. It spread to various towns
OL,16,Fand cities across the nation
OL,17,Fincluding, as we know, Tamworth.
