OL,4,Cuniform in post-Southport disorder
OL,6,F"A hotel in Tamworth housing asylum
OL,7,Fseekers was targeted, with significant
OL,8,Fdamage being caused and injuries
OL,9,Fsustained."
OL,11,FBell was someone who, through weight
OL,12,Fof numbers, had pursued an unlawful
OL,13,Fpurpose, the judge said, adding that
OL,14,Fshe had been among a group of about 20
OL,15,Fpeople believed to be heading towards
OL,16,Fa different hotel in the town.
OL,18,F"This is your first foray into the
OL,19,Fcriminal justice system," the judge
OL,20,Fsaid. "You have lost your job as a
OL,21,Fcarer."
