OL,6,FAcknowledging that Bell's involvement
OL,7,Fwas at about 10.30pm ` "after the
OL,8,Fworst was over" ` the judge said her
OL,9,Fcomments on the livestream were
OL,10,Funacceptable and abhorrent and had the
OL,11,F"potential to fan the flames".
OL,13,FRejecting calls for a suspended
OL,14,Fsentence, the judge concluded: "Anyone
OL,15,Finvolved in violent disorder must
OL,16,Fcommand immediate custody, with the
OL,17,Fneed for deterrence being acute."
